and there he came across this fundamental delusion about who we are remember that having decided having believing that we are human beings and heaven saying all want us to be happy no matter how you might define it if you ask any human being what they want they say I want to be happy and they might define in all sorts of different ways but that's what they want to be they want to be happy and that search for happiness

