leads to this acquisitiveness remember gathering things because the more you have of what you like the happier you seem to be you know the more money in the bank you feel safer etc etc and anything that undermines any of that of course is you want to get rid of so there's your aversion and if it's bigger than you then you run for it there's your fear so there's your the

