00:20:11,025 --> 00:20:12,567
You'll make the same mistake again.

163
00:20:13,968 --> 00:20:21,516
So this whole area of giving, it's reflecting on it, you see, and you give it.

164
00:20:21,737 --> 00:20:27,623
